          .col-sm-9
              .panel.panel-primary
                  .panel-heading 音を鳴らす
                  .panel-body
                      p
                          a.btn.btn-default(href='../demo/enchant/recipe2-8/index.html', target='_blank')
                              i.glyphicon.glyphicon-play
                              | デモ
